## 5. Open questions to user

**Q1 — First deliverable scope:**
- A: Quota reset learning + predicted next reset (recommended — smallest, foundational)
- B: Error taxonomy learning + per-class cooldowns
- C: Subscription-cost → $/MTok derivation (high QOL, small code surface)
- D: Self-healing v2 (anomaly + playbook)
- E: All four in one mega-PR (rejected by brainstorming skill)

**Q2 — Delivery path:**
- A: Pure upstream PR (cleanest, smallest blast radius)
- B: Fork-first, upstream-later (recommended for dogfooding)
- C: Hybrid — upstream extensibility hook PR + fork-only plugin (recommended for max upstream surface)
- D: Decide later (blocks spec)

